definitions.definition: To smoke marijuana in an enclosed space such as a car with the windows up.
definitions.label_groups: intransitive , slang , chiefly California , Northwestern US

definitions.definition: To enclose something and fill it with smoke by smoking (usually marijuana) inside it.
examples: We clambaked the car last night!
definitions.label_groups: transitive , slang , chiefly California , Northwestern US
